    <div id="features" class="section features">
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Features of EEMS</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <h3>User-Friendly Interface</h3>
                    <p>EEMS boasts an intuitive and user-friendly interface, making it easy for employees, managers, and finance teams to navigate and use the system efficiently.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Automated Expense Submission</h3>
                    <p>Employees can submit their expenses through a simple form, reducing paperwork and manual entry errors.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Multi-Tier Approval Workflow</h3>
                    <p>EEMS supports a multi-tier approval workflow, ensuring that expenses are reviewed and approved by the appropriate personnel at each level.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Real-Time Status Tracking</h3>
                    <p>Users can track the status of their submitted expenses in real-time, providing transparency and reducing follow-up queries.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Expense Categorization and Prioritization</h3>
                    <p>Expenses can be categorized and prioritized based on their type and urgency, helping manage budgets effectively.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>User Role Management</h3>
                    <p>Administrators can assign roles to users, granting different levels of access and functionality based on their responsibilities.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Payment Processing Integration</h3>
                    <p>EEMS integrates with payment processing systems to facilitate quick and secure reimbursements.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Detailed Financial Reporting</h3>
                    <p>Generate detailed financial reports to analyze expenses, track spending patterns, and make informed budget decisions.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Secure Authentication and Authorization</h3>
                    <p>Ensure data security with robust authentication and authorization mechanisms.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Audit Trail</h3>
                    <p>Maintain an audit trail of all transactions and activities within the system for compliance and accountability.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Cross-Platform Accessibility</h3>
                    <p>EEMS is accessible from any device with an internet connection, ensuring that users can manage their expenses on the go.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Scalability</h3>
                    <p>Scalable to accommodate growing organizations and increasing volumes of expense reports.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>System Integration</h3>
                    <p>Integrates with existing HR and financial systems for seamless data exchange and management.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Responsive Design</h3>
                    <p>Designed to be accessible across various devices, ensuring a consistent user experience on desktops, tablets, and smartphones.</p>
